{"tid":2020472,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"5.27 三罷好嗎","createTime":"2020-05-17T05:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T06:21:22.000Z","uid":192306,"like":14,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7c1dca39a5066d7ab7ba5c9ee915f441c28283a3","tid":2020472,"uid":192306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:45:05.000Z","msg":"5.27 日共歌法將再次放上立法會，進行二讀辯論。 繼早前的內會風波，兩辦發文干預內會事務，李慧琼強行主持會議。今次的共歌法二讀辯論，林奠政府勢必強行通過，無視一眾民意，將香港各位市民陷於水深火熱之中。大家試想一下，如果612我們沒有站出來，可以阻止送中惡法嗎？<br />\n<br />\n以表示我們對這次共歌法的不滿，我們 十八。連動 懇請各位香港人再次團結起來。我們<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呼籲各位香港人在5.27日放低手上的工作，參與大三罷</span></span>，向政府表達我們的不滿，並重申我們的决心。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，係時候歸隊了<br />\n5.27 大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HoDR84u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHoDR84u.jpg&h=f12376f8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gP4YO4v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgP4YO4v.jpg&h=d7ab1d7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47e3053d0d1233938901fd4c305449b284cd80b7","tid":2020472,"uid":192306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:45:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0ad5065bfed390a067b09c2d90c5f7c9e2ccd631","tid":2020472,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/KwZuaKq.gif\" />"},{"pid":"da3d3cbcd70209c8c4b5fd8437c062c65329b27b","tid":2020472,"uid":192306,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:46:11.000Z","msg":"國歌法殺到仲返工不了?"},{"pid":"c1f5d7024a053c22dbee0f453be083f30dae7e12","tid":2020472,"uid":11080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:46:51.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"75cc8abbe46523ce78860c1964efa79b72b757a9","tid":2020472,"uid":194746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:46:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ki